definitions.definition: A network of anastomosing or interwoven nerves , blood vessels , or lymphatic vessels .
An interwoven combination of parts or elements in a structure or system .

subdefinitions.definition: The system of equations required for the complete expression of the relations which exist between a set of quantities .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A network of anastomosing or interwoven nerves , blood vessels , or lymphatic vessels .
secondary_definitions: An interwoven combination of parts or elements in a structure or system .
